a482			; | BP ( u1 -- ) Enable or disable break point monitoring | DONE 
a482			; | | $00 Will enable the break points within specific code paths 
a482			; | | $01 Will disable break points 
a482			; | |  
a482			; | | By default break points are off. Either the above can be used to enable them 
a482			; | | or if a key is held down during start up the spashscreen will appear to freeze 
a482			; | | and on release of the pressed key the CONFIG menu will be displayed where you 
a482			; | | can disable break points. Exiting will then continue boot process. 
